  <title>PCManFM-&pcmanfm-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The PCManFM package contains an extremely fast, lightweight, yet
      feature-rich file manager with tabbed browsing.
    </para>

